{"_id":"4HmUOZBldJVpU3di","name":"Greater Mutations","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","results":[{"_id":"8zJDYwhuhbqQ4M0E","type":0,"text":"Arms of the Arheobear! - extend arm(s) to reach to ankles, knotted with muscle. Roll [[/roll 1d6]], 1-3 = one arm, 4-6 = all arms. +[[/roll 1d6]] damage with melee weapons wielded with affected arm.","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":1,"rangeH":1},{"_id":"giiCuIQmpv9AP7n6","type":0,"text":"Bestial Head - the twist's head turns into that of an animal or an alien.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"lJvic4vhu6gnMR3E","type":0,"text":"Boneless - the twist develops flexible bones, cartilage and viscera; halves all damage received from weapons, can squeeze through spaces 15cm in diameter. Can distend jaw to swallow unconscious or bound victims whole.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"8JpjPbNDBo8nli21","type":0,"text":"Blood Rage - the twist is subject to frenzy, doubling its weapon skill when instigating attacks but halving it when attacked.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"Hzo7OK9LAXdmxbpf","type":0,"text":"Breathes Miasma - once per round, as an extra attack action, the twist spews caustic vomit at an engaged opponent, inflicting [[/roll 1d6+3]] stamina damage that ignores armour.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"5ZCggnaoNA2fenYe","type":0,"text":"Warp Spawn - gains an additional [[/roll 1d3]] greater mutations.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"JQSzJ3XoLxsB50ut","type":0,"text":"Champion of arms - endowed with surpassing ferocity by the warp: +2 actions per round.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"9cD7GiJU0IbJALi3","type":0,"text":"Evil Eye - an extra eye in the forehead glowing with sickly light that scours and ruptures all it regards. Once per round, as an extra attack action, the twist may make a gaze attack, inflicting [[/roll 1d6+3]] stamina damage that ignores armour.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"cnNBcVjQDNGlCY3Q","type":0,"text":"Flyer - the twist is endowed with a functioning pair of wings they may glide or fly with.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"2qqSfZGbB6Rd6n0O","type":0,"text":"Gaping Maw - a cavernous, toothy mouth in the centre of the torso. An opponent inflicting a successful melee attack against this twist must make a successful dodge roll or be bitten for [[/roll 2d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10},{"_id":"d7Pe7Y3BnJ06lijz","type":0,"text":"Giant - the twist grows double in size and eight times the mass, with +2 to attack skill rolls, +[[/roll 1d6]] to damage rolls and +12 stamina.","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":11,"rangeH":11},{"_id":"SRc67Jjf2CdO5oih","type":0,"text":"Great Horns - may charge, attacking one opponent for [[/roll 3d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":12,"rangeH":12},{"_id":"HHnT2ie1zkXjVbH2","type":0,"text":"Hideous Appearance - endowed with a visage so horrific even aliens unused to human forms become uneasy. Torso and limbs composed of writhing tentacles, flesh putrid and rotting, hundreds of eyes and mouths, a voice that whispers the torment of a thousand screaming children - all in one twist, for example. The GM is encouraged to play this for all it is worth. Double adventuring skill total for Intimidate rolls.","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":13,"rangeH":13},{"_id":"utxVrOWc3QdN7moh","type":0,"text":"Horrible Stench - generates noxious body odour that can be smelled from the next field. Halve adventuring skill attempts at stealth and any social interaction except Intimidate.","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":14,"rangeH":14},{"_id":"MbhVUQBfD3W8Fbod","type":0,"text":"Leaper - grows prodigiously muscled legs. Can leap during action.","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":15,"rangeH":15},{"_id":"3z1XsrE6TQPbMVhA","type":0,"text":"Multiple Arms - the twist grows [[/roll 1d3]] extra arms and gains 1 extra attack action per round.","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":16,"rangeH":16},{"_id":"2ftr9LzzLAUiu8iE","type":0,"text":"Multiple Heads - the twist gains an additional head that chatters and bleats continually. When coordinated, gains an additional attack action per round. If one head can be distracted, thwarted or otherwise disengaged from its task the twist will fall into argument with itself, becoming unresponsive to anything other than life threatening circumstances for [[/roll 3d6]] minutes.","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":17,"rangeH":17},{"_id":"nPSpY32n7GaHH0N0","type":0,"text":"Poisonous Bite - the twist's bite is venomous doing [[/roll 1d2]] stamina damage and with the Poisonous quality.","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":18,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"AnF7LeVKvA6tO5jo","type":0,"text":"Prehensile Tail - capable of wielding a weapon, +1 attack action per round.","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":19,"rangeH":19},{"_id":"vKVU9zIaSdFDFAON","type":0,"text":"Blessed of the warp - the twist immediately gains access to [[/roll 1d6]] warp glyphs, and their warp focus skill increases by [[/roll 1d6]].","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":20,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AOG6LVsoaumRP9PT","name":"Lesser Mutations","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","results":[{"_id":"usroichK240tKBuq","type":0,"text":"Bestial Legs - legs transform to be fully bestial.","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":1,"rangeH":1},{"_id":"Rf4FZNIQMvfjWDGW","type":0,"text":"Cadaverous - the twist appears emaciated, halving adventuring Athletics and Endurance skills and suffering -1 to melee damage rolls.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"RWazV3d6Q5yegvoG","type":0,"text":"Colour - the twist gains unusual pigmentation of skin or fur. Roll [[/roll 1d6]] - 1: Albino, 2: Jet Black, 3: Sickly Green, 4: Blood Red, 5: Deep Purple, 6: Sky Blue.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"hu26vwTlPyEu1i1K","type":0,"text":"Crest - Wattle or crest instead of hair on head. Cosmetic.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"csVOTMNaPzZ7qiHX","type":0,"text":"Eye Stalks - [[/roll 3d6]] inches long. Cosmetic.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"ddk17ur6WIGvNf5d","type":0,"text":"Great Jaws - and savage teeth. May bite as its attack action for [[/roll 1d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"hCaPzG6r1XMwMqHi","type":0,"text":"Headless - head sinks slowly into the chest. Any critical strike to the head is ignored.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"qekWQX9Rn6WhKvTL","type":0,"text":"Hunchback - severe kyphosis. Cosmetic","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"YEVPfwoGwnFZY4FI","type":0,"text":"Huge Head - grows twice the size of normal, often ridged or horned. May headbutt as its attack action for [[/roll 1d6]] damage.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"A6CMT8tWekkRhXSR","type":0,"text":"Long neck - becomes 60 cm in length. Roll [[/roll 1d6]]: 1-3 = rigid, 4-6 = flexible.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10},{"_id":"7CEofzF4NFIejb8V","type":0,"text":"One eye - eyes fuse to a singular, cycloptic eye. Halve ranged attack roll results.","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":11,"rangeH":11},{"_id":"ceMiAwDIgklYcNIP","type":0,"text":"One leg - Legs fuse, the twist can hop at half speed, moving 2m as part of its action.","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":12,"rangeH":12},{"_id":"awPMyPsQ5eyWrMUO","type":0,"text":"Pin Head - sever microcephaly. Halves all weapon and adventuring skill roll results.","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":13,"rangeH":13},{"_id":"pWJynfn8rdxmMTSs","type":0,"text":"Quadraped - Arms extend to knees, twist may move on all fours.","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":14,"rangeH":14},{"_id":"FS43eY7fciqcT4kd","type":0,"text":"Rearranged limbs - Legs and arms swap. twist halves weapon and adventuring skill test results that require balance or gross motor competency.","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":15,"rangeH":15},{"_id":"FJRTQAwBIyD0wYmT","type":0,"text":"Tentacle arms - prehensile, cosmetic.","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":16,"rangeH":16},{"_id":"n2M3xixymhb40yfH","type":0,"text":"Third eye - roll [[/roll 1d6]] for location: 1: head, 2: arm, 3: torso, 4: groin, 5: buttock, 6: leg. Cosmetic.","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":17,"rangeH":17},{"_id":"isaBqHg7u9csxLkM","type":0,"text":"Tough skin - developes +1 armour. Roll [[/roll 1d6]] for type: 1: chitin, 2: quills, 3: dense fur, 4: thick leathery hide, 5: scales, 6: rubbery flesh.","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":18,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"sLBWiGcPgExvZ8jy","type":0,"text":"Marked by the warp - roll twice more on this table.","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":19,"rangeH":19},{"_id":"pXm1ZiqB5UzUIo2M","type":0,"text":"Chosen of the warp - roll once on the greater mutations table.","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":20,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JOgjUBGRbKWihwU6","name":"Critical - Crushing","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","results":[{"_id":"uQccnOm1qQoVTE7C","type":0,"text":"A rap on the skull sends teeth chattering, dazed for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"Aqv083gaBhGlcRr6","type":0,"text":"Foot crushed, hops around in agony for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"5yeATTyQ6kYdL33m","type":0,"text":"Dead leg, all tests involving movement at a penalty of -3 for [[/roll 1d3]] days.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"aWQMCSTnIJ5FNvXZ","type":0,"text":"A whack in the guts, winded and wheezing, can only defend at a penalty of -3 for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"0RSzMl4a6dKnJX1r","type":0,"text":"Hand crushed, determine which one (dominant/non-dominant). Drop what you were carrying and can't use hand for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"GGA9U5dVlspfFuKj","type":0,"text":"Thumped on the temples and seeing stars! Passes out for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"qfP4daeHOw3Zk493","type":0,"text":"Right in the kidney! Peeing blood, all tests at a penalty of -5 for the next [[/roll 1d6]] days. Better hope there is not too much internal bleeding!","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"iNRHCjALXcIaYvfw","type":0,"text":"Smack on the chin. Jaw fractured, slurred and garbled speech for [[/roll 1d6]] days. Broken and unsymmetrical face now.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"XlrfR0DdDMP7BpJo","type":0,"text":"Smashed on the skull and brained, dead.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iDtVH3INUBhf3YJX","name":"Critical - Piercing","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","results":[{"_id":"xBE4jAtytWJw2sKl","type":0,"text":"Right through the forearm, pass a sleight-of-hand test to keep hold of your weapon.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"icF77rnX0w3r25qp","type":0,"text":"A punctured rump! Very painful, all tests at a penalty of -3 for the next [[/roll 1d6]] rounds","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"0Y00s626yvvZXFGG","type":0,"text":"A hole in the guts, forces dinner up and over everyone. Spend [[/roll 1d6]] rounds retching, all actions are at a penalty of -3.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"58wdx01aX6uuHuWx","type":0,"text":"Right in the neck, can do nothing but gasp for breath and defend at a penalty of -2 for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"dBKMoXL8nvUWwfjV","type":0,"text":"Right through the shoulder, arm immobilised for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"VGRqrDhWkaBnuLfE","type":0,"text":"In the mouth! Teeth everywhere. Hard to talk through the blood, even uglier than before.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"FFmXRx3Uhk9v2PkJ","type":0,"text":"My eye! Permanent penalty of -2 to tests involving sight, ugly to boot.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"whYiF5ENfAsMZnNk","type":0,"text":"Pierced my hand! Drops weapon in pain. Hand a useless claw for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"FzO5koXwZX3pkKkP","type":0,"text":"Pierced through the heart or brain, dead.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kw4suXuB3lFPNHv5","name":"Critical - Energy","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","results":[{"_id":"5wCzvVcSMl8ze5IV","type":0,"text":"Hand burned! Drop your weapon and draw something else, quick!","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"uFVUHIgIYsWqa8Sz","type":0,"text":"Clothing on fire! Spend [[/roll 1d6]] rounds doing nothing except putting it out.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"3P9FJZmvMZjRtsOP","type":0,"text":"You gear catches fire! Either put it out for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, or let all that you own burn!","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"3VZ1wIwM1cqIXKDw","type":0,"text":"Breathe in the fumes, coughing and spluttering for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, all tests at a penalty of -3.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"w4utDAoV27AZCryE","type":0,"text":"Blinded by the blast, permanent penalty of -2 to tests involving sight.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"FgSUMhQ3Sv8XVbsA","type":0,"text":"Knocked off your feet and flung against the wall. Stunned and prone for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, all tests at a penalty of -3.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"eX51YO7bQnMpIpp7","type":0,"text":"Hair singed off, scalp red and raw. No hats or helmets for [[/roll 1d6]] days, all tests at penalty of -3 during this time.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"h0AYsC9V1Ejhdbw9","type":0,"text":"Full in the face, the blast destroys your sense of smell. All tests involving smell at a penalty of -3, now your companions are more bearable.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"71XkLZK8gk6QoSTR","type":0,"text":"Skin and bone seared, dead.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qeA5y0TqNeHApGdC","name":"Critical - Slashing","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","results":[{"_id":"gIToj6uho6m3ubW1","type":0,"text":"Slashed across the skull, dazed for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, all actions at a penalty of 2. Double vision for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"COMbknprx2nxfROr","type":0,"text":"Slashed on the hip, falls over and can only crawl in the dirt for [[/roll 1d6]] rounds, all tests at a penalty of -3.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"SCm7AqlSmYmK3kFV","type":0,"text":"Cut on thigh, can only hobble for [[/roll 1d3]] days, Endurance test not to end up with a limp.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"7jh4eLYZqTy4674B","type":0,"text":"That was my foot! Can only hobble for [[/roll 1d6]] days. Toes loose in the boot.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"PYWAPiqMW6kb1KeZ","type":0,"text":"Slash on the back, opening muscles, can't carry a pack for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"oisIoyH4C8OMYnXc","type":0,"text":"Whoops, [[/roll 1d3]] fingers sliced off, randomly determine hand, drop what you're carrying.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"NinLGTP3srFweh5G","type":0,"text":"An ear is slashed! Permanent penalty of -2 to tests involving hearing.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"FXiAQNj5laLfj2SR","type":0,"text":"Hacked in the shoulder! Determine which arm, tests involving that arm are at a penalty of -5 for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"a53LCjzDxfP4oTyh","type":0,"text":"Cut through an artery, dead.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"z1hXYx7O38iO41kz","name":"Warp Bleed","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/items/spells/wind-hole.svg","results":[{"_id":"pBt1Dry6YAe5URSJ","type":0,"text":"The caster's hands catch fire causing them [[/roll 1d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":1,"rangeH":1},{"_id":"DZ0jZ06tJqz4oezb","type":0,"text":"Two mindless tentacles grow from the user's body for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"ykf9gq3KnkoV9Jmf","type":0,"text":"One of the caster's eyes turns milky white.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"81BekGTo992y5JKr","type":0,"text":"The glyph discharges incorrectly, hitting the nearest creature for [[/roll 2d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"RABPgDuVmldt0XKv","type":0,"text":"The caster vomits acidic ectoplasm on all nearby causing [[/roll 1d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"qG0KtpxK36Fw7fSS","type":0,"text":"Blood runs from the eyes for [[/roll 1d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"2Cs64Pz4evCOzuA8","type":0,"text":"The glyph backfires, blasting the caster across the room for [[/roll 2d6]] stamina damage.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"7lIFfgzOfTWqDHMy","type":0,"text":"The caster loses the sense of taste, all food is like ash.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"woU3zsT1lNBuDQe7","type":0,"text":"The caster's skin is bleached white.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"SRaGA61YhH1nOxMg","type":0,"text":"All of the caster's hair falls out.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10},{"_id":"3ekA27uszXiuyibq","type":0,"text":"The caster's skin becomes translucent for [[/roll 2d6]] days.","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":11,"rangeH":11},{"_id":"NcUnYuf2B3erComo","type":0,"text":"The caster's arms are altered, growing small bone spurs.","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":12,"rangeH":12},{"_id":"upKNdP0KUim3YOHr","type":0,"text":"The caster freezes like a statue for the next [[/roll 1d3]] days.","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":13,"rangeH":13},{"_id":"YYunmiUjkiH1Ukax","type":0,"text":"A miasma of warp energies fill a nearby space, causing [[/roll 1d6+2]] stamina damage to all.","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":14,"rangeH":14},{"_id":"x7liRdZmTQOQRdsn","type":0,"text":"The caster's eyes turn jet black for [[/roll 1d6]] weeks.","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":15,"rangeH":15},{"_id":"Zel5SFBMiPJlz8TP","type":0,"text":"The caster is possessed by a malevolent warp being for [[/roll 1d6]] turns.","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":16,"rangeH":16},{"_id":"GuSDv2PShV3UlK3p","type":0,"text":"The caster loses the ability to manifest glyphs for [[/roll 1d6]] days, every attempt causes warp bleed.","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":17,"rangeH":17},{"_id":"wXKOhnRV4YhVBUSi","type":0,"text":"The user gains a minor warp mutation.","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":18,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"m0oGZh6pBAIgCtzL","type":0,"text":"The user gains a major warp mutation.","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":19,"rangeH":19},{"_id":"2xd65snpcvYTlZVj","type":0,"text":"The user is swallowed by the warp!","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":20,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
